features.text:
Just Overblown (part 1)

I wonder now
what’s your word if you can’t bring thunder now
if ya can’t bring the terror down
ya Caint stop the horror now
so what
walk the purist route 
hype ya game on the clout route
taking fame cause ya bow down
what if I take it all now 
who gives a damn 
I’m labelled sham 
thank you maam
thank you god here’s to another holiday in a studio alone 
while they puke on the throne 
while they dress like a clone
why they spy like a drone
when they full grown 
I just stand on my own 
the other shit just overblown

I was so deep in love then 
my heart wasn’t mine it was hers then 
she just fucked some other man didn’t tell me
did tell me i was toxic, DAMN
can’t excuse so many mood swings 
when we gotta do the damn thing 
ain’t a choice unless we starve
aint no time to crash the car
just a time to travel far
descendants from the stars
you done said so many things 
you just broke so many dreams
I expect the boy to dream
don’t expect the boy to scream
he already took the ring
amazing
he’s so much more amazing 
ducking bullets that would graze him
that’s a friend worth fighting for
I adore 
souls worth saving 
your own
that other shit just overblown

Just Overblown (part 2)

I couldn’t dream so many fears
I couldn’t walk with no intention clear
how do you run with all that fiction 
how you crossing up your diction 
how do you bring such madness
how you lay the land to barren sadness
I’m adotmays aint got that DNA
aint got the chromosome 
your on your own 
Aint got no time to call the boss
you in the cracks like dental floss
no time to fake I see the albatross
high above miami like that hawk 
you just aren’t seeing
they call it mental health 
I call it fleeing
they ask many things
I just can’t see it 
can’t see the boundary lines
I release the dove
release the rhyme 
wound is sewn 
other shit just overblown

here’s a shout for days was sunny
did it all made a little money 
broke barriers
while they sell carriers
barks like terriers
why ya staring 
in pure hysteria
I seen boundaries removed
seen tragedy what could I do 
did things they said I couldn’t 
won at things they said I shouldn’t
they propped their ego while instilling doubt
hollywood cutout
ran the mouth instilling doubt
hater lingo 
played like bingo 
it’s 2021 
I’m done
they shown 
the other shit 
Just overblown
